snippet.title: HAWK: Freedom Squadron - Trailer EN
snippet.description:
Download and Play Now: http://apple.co/2nw0LSM

Grab your bros and plunge yourself into a breathtaking, fast-paced combat action! Together, you'll protect the country of Verdia against merciless invaders in a campaign spanning 100+ missions. Casually join an endless arcade mode or lead hardcore raids with whole squadrons at your disposal, and more!
